text: Karel Matoušek (born 10 May 1928) is a Czech wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman lightweight at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1928 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Czech male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Czechoslovakia Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Prague
